text:
Furthermore, what is the purpose of killing me? If you are killing me
for meat, even though the [meat of] animals with five nails may be eaten,
the flesh of a monkey should not be eaten.

The nature of a ksatriya is my guidance. It is not hinsa (murder) to kill
any animal. All the ksatriyas in the [foregone] past I take as example;
they did not sin.
